{"tid":2074121,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"研究發現：感染武肺後人類抗體僅持續2-3月，或增加疫苗研發難度","createTime":"2020-06-22T00:58:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-22T09:36:30.000Z","uid":48040,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"006726509a2a7bb22042e01d3a17fa6cfb3f4945","tid":2074121,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T00:58:37.000Z","msg":"《自然&middot;醫學》期刊：<br />\n<br />\n感染新冠病毒後患者體內的抗體水平兩到三個月後便開始下降。<br />\n<br />\n耶魯大學病毒免疫學家Akiko Iwasaki擔憂，由於疫苗的原理是使接種者產生中和抗體以抵禦病毒，如果自然感染產生的抗體微弱且短期，<span style=\"color: orange;\">那麼疫苗或許需要比病毒&ldquo;更強&rdquo;</span>。這會為疫苗開髮帶來難度。<br />\n<br />\n簡單講：<br />\n武肺病毒令人體產生的抗體並唔多。如果人類想開發疫苗，令人體產生足夠的抗體，<span style=\"color: orange;\">就需要先將武肺病毒改造到更加犀利</span>，然後滅活，再注射入人體，才可產生足夠抗體。武漢病毒研究所又大派用場啦！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.caixin.com/2020-06-22/101570542.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.caixin.com%2F2020-06-22%2F101570542.html&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0FwjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=7db337ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.caixin.com/2020-06-22/101570542.html</a><br />\n<br />\n======<br />\n黃channel撐得好辛苦，可以幫手subscribe嗎？<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/e7Q0NLD83eI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fe7Q0NLD83eI&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0FwjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=a0e209ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/e7Q0NLD83eI</a>"},{"pid":"1f869b5b0453e08f26ec1db0e191ba5a5cb028b7","tid":2074121,"uid":74622,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T00:59:54.000Z","msg":"夏天唔想再戴口罩"},{"pid":"2b277f30e3f8f949776337930eb3c4eeff33eee2","tid":2074121,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f869b5b0453e08f26ec1db0e191ba5a5cb028b7","tid":2074121,"uid":74622,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T00:59:54.000Z","msg":"夏天唔想再戴口罩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T01:01:58.000Z","msg":"有排捱"},{"pid":"ee25d02fcdd774932d2b95bf82fa85cad99c9435","tid":207412