s/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一打唔使找<br />\n<br />\n你連隻vaccine點運作都唔識就係度鳩噏"},{"pid":"78014ba92ebc916442bd0e8b64ef4856a7370e51","tid":2074121,"uid":48130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T09:29:40.000Z","msg":"每日n篇假新聞重想人地比錢你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"4e4ba1e9693dacccbd14a0c204b0c99cd02b3cfc","tid":2074121,"uid":48040,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T01:05:48.000Z","msg":"劇情可能係：某國為咗爭取成為第一個成為研發疫苗的國家（為名為利），開發更加強的病毒，點知再次洩漏，釀成更大災難。無限Loop。"}}